title: Rubrik stock rips 25% higher after blowing out earnings and boosting guidance
description: Rubrik CEO Bipul Sinha told CNBC that his company's cyber resilience products and new tools for AI agents are helping fuel growth.
content:
Rubrik shares soared 25% on Friday after the data management company posted blowout third-quarter numbers and boosted guidance.
